description:
“In the beginning the universe will return to its initial point”
“In the beginning everything will return back”
“ In the beginning everything will start again”

the circular line that gives life to a sphere that melts, shows us a metaphorical universe that moves and returns to its place of origin, at the beginning of everything.
This generative art explores the line as the main element of its structure being shaped by audio frequencies.
*** For a better audio appreciation, listen in a subwoofer (or good bass) audio system
